      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. It looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership, with a flawless exterior finish and an interior that still smells new. Every mechanical component is in perfect working order, and it comes with a complete, documented service history showing no expense was spared in its maintenance. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a used car that is truly indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
