    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready for its next adventure? This reliable ride is a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a solid vehicle at a great price! While it shows some honest cosmetic wear and signs of its many successful journeys, it still runs strong and offers a comfortable, practical driving experience for your everyday needs.",
