    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic repairs to be safely returned to the road. The engine currently suffers from significant oil leaks and a rough idle, indicating potential internal issues that need professional diagnosis. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the rear passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a donor vehicle for parts.",
