    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. Meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and strictly hand-washed, the exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, scratch, or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every dashboard switch operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists. This vehicle comes complete with all original keys, factory manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the buyer who demands perfection and an investment-grade example, this car stands as a benchmark of its kind.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
